  "Description": {
    "English": "An eye of living stone: waiting, watching. A relic left by a slumbering guardian, keeping sentry over ancient creature burial grounds.<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Disturbing the eye may disturb the slumber of <span class=\"name name-special\">living stone guardians</span>. Ensure re-animated guardians are defeated before storing this relic in the home.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "活石的眼睛：永远在等待与监视。一位沉睡的守护者留下的遗物，这个眼睛永远守护着远古生物的埋葬地。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：惊动眼睛有可能会唤醒沉睡的<span class=\"name name-special\">活石守护者</span>。将这件遗物放入家中之前，请确保你已经打败所有复苏的守护者。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "活石頭之眼：持續等待、持續觀察。這是沉睡的守護者留下的遺物，它持續警戒著古老生物的埋葬地。<br><br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：擾亂眼睛的視線可能會打擾到<span class=\"name name-special\">活石頭守護者</span>的沉睡。在把這個遺物帶回家之前，請務必先擊敗回復活動的守護者。"
  },
